You did a good job keeping it a secret.

92
00:05:37,670 --> 00:05:38,920
Come clean.

93
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:40,110
When did you two start?

94
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,080
Who pursued who?

95
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:43,040
This calls for

96
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,280
