107
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,240
Plans change.

108
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,120
It's okay.

109
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,920
I can wait for you here.

110
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:22,480
Boss doesn't seem happy, does he?

111
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,680
Lin Meina,

112
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,800
