to be with her?

120
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,600
Originally, I really
didn't have any feelings for her.

121
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,640
But after seeing her alone last time,

122
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:58,920
I found out she had a completely
different side.

123
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,760
Cool,

124
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,320
elegant,

125
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,480
and very charming.

126
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,680
You've

127
