serious?

135
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,400
I used to only know work,

136
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,520
didn't know what love was.

137
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,040
But now I realize,

138
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,440
