139
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,800
it can't be stopped.

140
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,400
Moreover, Ye Ran likes me so much.

141
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,280
We belong to each other.

142
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,920
We should seize the opportunity.

143
